room_title: Escape room "Trapped in a Room with a Zombie" by Ninja Escape in Seattle
room_description: There is one hungry zombie chained to the wall. Every 5 minutes a buzzer sounds & the chain grows a foot from the wall! In 60 minutes the zombie will be able to reach you, so you have to find the ultimate key to freedom or join the walking dead! Can you outwit a brain-dead zombie?
